Jan 2024 05:16:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-urges-china-help-curb-red-sea-attacks-by-iran-backed-houthis-ft-2024-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟制定经济安全计划 关注中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/eu-draws-up-economic-security-plans-with-mind-china-2024-01-24/</link><description>欧盟委员会将于周三制定计划，通过对外国投资进行更严格的审查以及对向中国等竞争对手的出口和技术外流进行更严格的控制来加强欧盟的经济安全。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 05:04:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/eu-draws-up-economic-security-plans-with-mind-china-2024-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>独家：特斯拉计划于 2025 年中期生产新款电动汽车</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-plans-build-new-electric-vehicles-mid-2025-sources-2024-01-24/</link><description>据四位知情人士透露，特斯拉已告知供应商，希望在 2025 年中期开始生产一款代号为“Redwood”的新型大众市场电动汽车，其中两人将该车型描述为紧凑型跨界车。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 05:03:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-plans-build-new-electric-vehicles-mid-2025-sources-2024-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>前台湾盟友瑙鲁与中国恢复外交关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-nauru-re-establish-diplomatic-ties-state-media-2024-01-24/</link><description>中国和瑙鲁周三重新建立了外交关系，此前这个太平洋小岛国出人意料地断绝了与其前盟友台湾的关系，美国称此举“不幸”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 04:32:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-nauru-re-establish-diplomatic-ties-state-media-2024-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>碧桂园寻求出售广州价值5.3亿美元的资产</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/country-garden-seeks-sell-assets-worth-530-mln-guangzhou-2024-01-24/</link><description>据资产交易平台称，陷入困境的中国房地产开发商碧桂园正在广州出售房产，旨在筹集 38 亿元人民币（5.3 亿美元）的资金。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 03:41:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/country-garden-seeks-sell-assets-worth-530-mln-guangzhou-2024-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国监管部门要求基金遏制股指期货卖空行为</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-regulators-ask-funds-restrict-short-selling-stock-index-futures-sources-2024-01-24/</link><description>两名消息人士称，中国证券监管机构已要求一些对冲基金经理限制股指期货市场的卖空行为，以稳定正在下跌的股票。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 03:24:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-regulators-ask-funds-restrict-short-selling-stock-index-futures-sources-2024-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>2023年中国城镇新增就业1244万人，称今年需加大力度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-adds-1244-mln-urban-jobs-2023says-more-effort-needed-this-year-2024-01-24/</link><description>中国人力资源部周三在新闻发布会上表示，去年中国城镇新增就业1244万人，实现了目标，但在2024年经济形势不确定的情况下，需要加大力度支撑就业。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 03:23:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-adds-1244-mln-urban-jobs-2023says-more-effort-needed-this-year-2024-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>日本12月出口飙升至创纪录水平；中国出货量出现期待已久的反弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/japan-exports-soar-record-dec-china-shipments-make-long-awaited-rebound-2024-01-24/</link><description>日本12月出口飙升至历史新高，其中对美国的出口飙升至历史最高水平，对中国的出口也强劲，创下一年多以来的首次增长。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 03:20:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/japan-exports-soar-record-dec-china-shipments-make-long-awaited-rebound-2024-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>潜在的中国救助方案提振情绪，亚洲股市上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-01-24/</link><description>亚洲股市周三上涨，因市场乐观地认为中国当局将为已跌至多年低点的股市提供支持，而日本央行的鹰派倾向提振了日元。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 03:00:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>美联储观点推动美元徘徊在六周高位附近；日本央行推动日元小幅上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-hovers-near-6-week-high-fed-view-yen-edges-up-after-boj-2024-01-24/</link><description>周三，美元兑主要货币徘徊在六周高点附近，因投资者强化了美联储在美国经济强劲的情况下不会急于降息的预期。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 01:32:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-hovers-near-6-week-high-fed-view-yen-edges-up-after-boj-2024-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾称武装部队将确保南海“畅通无阻、和平”的勘探</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-says-armed-forces-ensure-unimpeded-peaceful-exploration-south-china-2024-01-24/</link><description>马尼拉国防部长表示，随着菲律宾将重点转向对外防御，菲律宾武装部队将保证在该国专属经济区（EEZ）内“不受阻碍、和平”地勘探和开采自然资源。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 01:27:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-says-armed-forces-ensure-unimpeded-peaceful-exploration-south-china-2024-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国表示欧盟“不公平”的电动汽车补贴调查可能会损害两国关系 - 彭博社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-says-eus-unfair-ev-subsidies-probe-risks-damaging-ties-bloomberg-news-2024-01-24/</link><description>傅聪在接受彭博社采访时表示，中国驻欧盟大使称欧盟对中国电动汽车制造商国家补贴的调查“不公平”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 01:15:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-says-eus-unfair-ev-subsidies-probe-risks-damaging-ties-bloomberg-news-2024-01-24/</guid></item></channel></rss>